{"tid":2377361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大灣區青年就業計劃，勞工處上載130個空缺","createTime":"2021-01-23T14:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:35:19.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"caa174581a7e5d72ec8163264dfc70ee19097a25","tid":2377361,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421423&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TavSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=327248cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421423&h=885689d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421423</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】施政報告提出大灣區青年就業計劃，勞工處最新資料顯示有130個職位空缺。<br />\n<br />\n大部分內地工作地點在深圳，亦有東莞、廣州與江門等，月薪介乎1.8萬至2.8萬元，但未有列明食宿安排。創科相關職位佔56個，內地科網企業騰訊就提供超過30個空缺；其他一般職位有財務助理、業務拓展及法律顧問等，有教育服務公司聘請教師到江門市，以普通話任教香港文憑試課程。<br />\n<br />\n大灣區青年就業計劃共有2000個名額，當中700個是創科職位，月薪不得低於1.8萬元。政府會向參與企業提供1萬元津貼，為期18個月。"},{"pid":"84f333fad2ae431b8f633a86a88df60de83e424f","tid":2377361,"uid":20867,"like":15,"dislike":21,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2ETKPG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2ETKPG.png&h=3a7a8c58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d8f4fe4136df88bb56ac2ee55e410cbd5e0f2b7","tid":2377361,"uid":36995,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"交稅都無左你兩成 -4000<br />\n仲要租間似樣既屋 -4000<br />\n入袋得既錢得一皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d029ede962b52cbc787d319ed76b1c1a0ce1bd","tid":2377361,"uid":194281,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:21:10.000Z","msg":"所謂空缺根本係假位,一間連鎖舖POST幾十個職位<br />\n實際上唔請人"},{"pid":"0dda6221eab7b3eefc257144c317741a0e3797b6","tid":23